graph TD
    A[Upload File] --> B[Detect MIME Type]
    B --> C{Check Quota?}
    C -- No --> D[Quota Exceeded - Notify User]
    C -- Yes --> E[Store File in Storage Service]
    E --> F[Index File in Search Engine]
    F --> G[Access File: Preview / Download]
    G --> H{Optional: Send by Email to Client?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Compose & Send Email]
    I --> J[Log Activity]
    H -- No --> J
    D --> K((End))
    J --> K